snippet.textDisplay:
3:06 Kashmiri Vanvun prayers recreated by Coke Studio Bharat. Vanvun is a mix of prayers and blessings by relatives and families for bride and bridegroom during marriage. Vanvun is also sung during other family functions and celebrations. An oral tradition from Kashmir kept alive since centuries. Celebrating kashmiri culture & making kashmir proud💖
This really gave goosebumps🔥 
Hats off @cokestudiobharat 👏
